  87:3:2:"The second word of verse (87:3) is a form II perfect verb (<span class=\"at\">فعل ماض</span>). The verb is third person masculine singular. The verb's triliteral root is <i class=\"ab\">qāf dāl rā</i> (<span class=\"at\">ق د ر</span>)."
