  87:4:2:"The second word of verse (87:4) is a form IV perfect verb (<span class=\"at\">فعل ماض</span>). The verb is third person masculine singular. The verb's triliteral root is <i class=\"ab\">khā rā jīm</i> (<span class=\"at\">خ ر ج</span>)."
